title: Daz3D - Genesis 2 Female Morphs
description:
A required item for one of the other Daz3D torrents I recently uploaded.  

Description: Genesis 2 Female(s) Morphs Bundle includes both head and body morphs.

The concept of Daz morphing has been advanced further in the Genesis 2 product line. With more points of articulation, more polygons in the figures, and male and female specific bases, Genesis 2 allows you to sculpt Victoria 6, and any Genesis 2 3D model figure into more detailed, more articulate and more gender specific forms. Take advantage of all Genesis 2's customization features with this complete head and body morphing bundle.

Reference link: http://www.daz3d.com/new-releases/genesis-2-female-morphs-bundle

What's included: 
    Genesis 2 Female Head Morphs
    Genesis 2 Female Body Morphs 

This torrent appears to also include "Victoria 4 for Genesis 2 Female"

Description: Generation 6, meet Generation 4! Victoria 4 for the Genesis 2 Female, premiere 3D models, gives you a path to use your existing Victoria 4 accessories and textures on your Genesis 2 Female characters. Use the AutoFit clone to access your favorite outfits, the Victoria 4 UV set to use your favorite textures and the Victoria 4 figure shape to see a familiar face.

note: Due to a limitation in how DAZ Studio handles presets, only material presets which are in DUF format can be directly applied. Any existing material presets must be re-saved in DUF format from the original Victoria 4.

Reference link: http://www.daz3d.com/new-releases/victoria-4-for-genesis-2-female

Damn if I know what all this does.  I'm still learning it.
